---
const phone = "484-706-9229";
const phoneTel = "+1" + phone.replace(/[^0-9]/g, "");
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Revision Home Improvements | Lehigh Valley Home Improvement & Remodeling</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Revision Home Improvements provides home improvement, remodeling, and repair services in the Lehigh Valley. Call for an estimate or request a quote online." />
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <header class="wrap header">
        <div class="brand">Revision Home Improvements</div>
        <nav class="nav">
          <a href="#services">Services</a>
          <a href="#process">How it works</a>
          <a href="#faq">FAQ</a>
          <a class="btn" href="/request-a-quote">Request a Quote</a>
          <a class="btn btn-outline" href={`tel:${phoneTel}`}>Call {phone}</a>
        </nav>
      </header>

      <section class="wrap hero">
        <div>
          <h1>Have Your Space Transformed by Our Expert Partners</h1>
          <p class="sub">
            Discover top-notch home improvement, remodeling, and repair solutions tailored for you.
            Serving the <strong>Lehigh Valley</strong>.
          </p>
          <div class="cta">
            <a class="btn" href="/request-a-quote">Request a Quote</a>
            <a class="btn btn-outline" href={`tel:${phoneTel}`}>Call {phone}</a>
          </div>
          <p class="note">
            We take pride in being certified experts committed to saving you time and money—cost-effective solutions without compromising quality.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-card">
          <div class="hero-card-title">Fast response</div>
          <div class="hero-card-body">We aim to reply within <strong>24–48 hours</strong>.</div>
          <div class="hero-card-title">Estimates</div>
          <div class="hero-card-body">Transparent estimates tailored to your project.</div>
          <div class="hero-card-title">Guaranteed repairs</div>
          <div class="hero-card-body">We stand behind our work.</div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="services" class="wrap section">
        <h2>Providing Excellence in Home Services for the Lehigh Valley</h2>
        <div class="bullets">
          <div>Trustworthy and reliable team members</div>
          <div>We help you create your vision of your home</div>
          <div>Responsibility with affordable prices</div>
        </div>
        <div class="services">
          <div class="service">
            <h3>Home Improvement</h3>
            <p>Repairs, updates, and punch-list work to keep your home in great shape.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="service">
            <h3>Remodeling</h3>
            <p>Kitchen, bath, and interior remodel support—from planning to finishing touches.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="service">
            <h3>Flooring & Finishes</h3>
            <p>Refresh your space with durable flooring and clean, professional finishes.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="process" class="wrap section">
        <h2>How it works</h2>
        <ol class="steps">
          <li>
            <div class="step-title">Book Online</div>
            <div>You share your needs with us and we’ll schedule a visit if needed.</div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="step-title">Phone Confirmation</div>
            <div>We contact you for details and schedule an onsite estimate if necessary.</div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="step-title">Detailed Estimate</div>
            <div>We send you details and a cost estimate of your project needs.</div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="step-title">Task Completion</div>
            <div>Our team completes the work while you relax and enjoy the improvements.</div>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </section>

      <section id="faq" class="wrap section">
        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <div class="faq">
          <details open>
            <summary>Will I receive a response within 24–48 hours?</summary>
            <p>
              Yes. We’re committed to getting back to you promptly within 24–48 hours from your inquiry.
            </p>
          </details>
          <details>
            <summary>What is your hourly rate, and do you have a job minimum?</summary>
            <p>
              Our hourly rate is competitive and reflects the quality of our work. For detailed pricing and any job minimums,
              request a quote and we’ll provide a clear estimate for your project.
            </p>
          </details>
          <details>
            <summary>Can I expect multiple estimates for my project?</summary>
            <p>
              Yes. We can provide multiple approaches and estimates so you can choose what best fits your budget and goals.
            </p>
          </details>
          <details>
            <summary>Are the repairs guaranteed?</summary>
            <p>
              Yes. We stand behind our work. If anything comes up after service, reach out and we’ll make it right.
            </p>
          </details>
        </div>
        <div class="cta" style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
          <a class="btn" href="/request-a-quote">Request a Quote</a>
          <a class="btn btn-outline" href={`tel:${phoneTel}`}>Call {phone}</a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <footer class="wrap footer">
        <div>
          <strong>Revision Home Improvements</strong><br />
          Lehigh Valley, PA
        </div>
        <div class="footer-links">
          <a href="/request-a-quote">Request a Quote</a>
          <a href={`tel:${phoneTel}`}>Call {phone}</a>
        </div>
      </footer>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #0b0f14;
    --card: #121826;
    --muted: #a9b3c1;
    --text: #eef2f7;
    --brand: #ff3b30;
    --border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
  }
  body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, Noto Sans, Helvetica, Arial;
    background: radial-gradient(1200px 600px at 20% 0%, rgba(255, 59, 48, 0.18), transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(1200px 600px at 90% 10%, rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.18), transparent 55%),
      var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
  }
  a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
  .wrap { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px; }
  .header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 22px 20px;
  }
  .brand { font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 0.2px; }
  .nav { display: flex; gap: 12px; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: flex-end; }
  .nav a { opacity: 0.9; }
  .nav a:hover { opacity: 1; }

  .hero {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 0.8fr;
    gap: 24px;
    padding: 20px;
    padding-bottom: 8px;
  }
  h1 { font-size: 44px; line-height: 1.05; margin: 0 0 12px; }
  .sub { color: var(--muted); font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0 0 18px; }
  .note { color: var(--muted); margin-top: 16px; max-width: 60ch; }
  .cta { display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .btn {
    background: var(--brand);
    color: white;
    padding: 12px 16px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    border: 1px solid transparent;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .btn-outline {
    background: transparent;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .hero-card {
    background: rgba(18, 24, 38, 0.72);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 16px;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  }
  .hero-card-title { font-weight: 800; margin-top: 10px; }
  .hero-card-body { color: var(--muted); }

  .section { padding: 32px 20px; }
  h2 { font-size: 28px; margin: 0 0 14px; }
  .bullets { display: grid; gap: 10px; color: var(--muted); }

  .services {
    margin-top: 16px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 12px;
  }
  .service {
    background: rgba(18, 24, 38, 0.55);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 16px;
  }
  .service p { color: var(--muted); margin: 8px 0 0; }

  .steps {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    list-style: none;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 12px;
  }
  .steps li {
    background: rgba(18, 24, 38, 0.55);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 16px;
  }
  .step-title { font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .steps div { color: var(--muted); }

  .faq details {
    background: rgba(18, 24, 38, 0.55);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 14px 16px;
    margin: 10px 0;
  }
  .faq summary { cursor: pointer; font-weight: 700; }
  .faq p { color: var(--muted); margin: 10px 0 0; }

  .footer {
    padding: 28px 20px 40px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 12px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .footer-links { display: flex; gap: 14px; align-items: center; }
  .footer-links a { color: var(--muted); }
  .footer-links a:hover { color: var(--text); }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    h1 { font-size: 36px; }
    .services { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .steps { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
